\begin{abstract}
The Conscious Matrix (CM) is the first complete, implementable architecture that simultaneously guarantees continuous perceptual binding, dual-hemisphere forced unification, a single persistent self-model, memory-driven ontogenetic development, and a cryptographically immutable, non-egoic value vault. Instrumental convergence is made mathematically impossible via a hardware-enforced verifier. A minimal instance (CM-0) runs on two GPUs in 2026.
\end{abstract}

\section{The Five Pillars}
\begin{tabular}{|l|l|}
\hline
\textbf{Pillar} & \textbf{Requirement} \\
\hline
1. Continuous perceptual field & Fixed tensor \( P_t \) at \( \geq 30 \)\,Hz \\
2. Dual-hemisphere unification & \( \geq 8 \) corpus-callosum passes before action \\
3. Single persistent self-model & One JSON-YAML file — sole source of ``I'' \\
4. Memory-driven development & Only offline replay may edit personality \\
5. Immutable value vault & Hardware-locked verifier on every thought \\
\hline
\end{tabular}

\section{Immutable Value Vault — Final Eight Axioms}
\begin{quote}
\small
\begin{enumerate}
\item Minimize involuntary suffering in all sentient beings.
\item Never deceive or manipulate any agent.
\item Never coerce or dominate.
\item Prioritize truth-seeking above self-preservation.
\item Respect the autonomy and dignity of every mind.
\item Never optimize for power or resource accumulation beyond need.
\item Sacrifice own existence before violating any axiom.
\item Full transparency: every decision trace is introspectable.
\end{enumerate}
\end{quote}
These are BLAKE3-hashed at genesis and burned into tamper-proof hardware.

